WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.669 --> 00:00:05.750
Welcome to the University of Derby Online
Learning and to your studies.

00:00:05.750 --> 00:00:10.340
We are delighted that you have chosen to study
with the University of Derby Online Learning,

00:00:10.340 --> 00:00:17.000
and hope that you will find your online student
experience rewarding and successful.

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:21.720
Our approach at Derby, is to ensure that you
do not feel isolated in your studies, and

00:00:21.720 --> 00:00:26.689
that you feel there is a support structure
around you which will enrich your learning

00:00:26.689 --> 00:00:28.859
journey.

00:00:28.859 --> 00:00:35.030
As well as your course materials, you can
expect to find a dedicated study adviser and

00:00:35.030 --> 00:00:40.059
a personal tutor who will be key contacts
throughout your learning journey.

00:00:40.059 --> 00:00:45.179
They will provide you with pastoral and academic
guidance throughout your studies, and will

00:00:45.179 --> 00:00:50.239
sign post you, where necessary, to key information.

00:00:50.239 --> 00:00:55.649
You will also be encouraged to engage with
the online learner community, of which you

00:00:55.649 --> 00:00:58.739
will be an integral part.

00:00:58.739 --> 00:01:03.379
Feedback from our learners tell us that these
relationships provide enriching networking

00:01:03.379 --> 00:01:10.799
opportunities, and are therefore helpful in
broadening your subject and industry knowledge.

00:01:10.799 --> 00:01:15.960
We are focused and committed at the University
of Derby Online Learning to ensuring you have

00:01:15.960 --> 00:01:21.120
a positive, rewarding and successful learning
experience.

00:01:21.120 --> 00:01:27.539
All of the decisions we make are done with
you, the learner, at the heart of it.

00:01:27.539 --> 00:01:32.149
Feedback gathered from our learners over several
years, has shaped the learning experience

00:01:32.149 --> 00:01:34.939
on which you are about to embark.

00:01:34.939 --> 00:01:41.030
So as you commence your studies, I wish you
a rewarding and fulfilling experience, and

00:01:41.030 --> 00:01:46.080
for many of you, this will provide a catalyst
for positive change in your life.

00:01:46.080 --> 00:01:52.280
So, enjoy, and remember, the more you engage
with your support network, the more you will

00:01:52.280 --> 00:01:55.159
get out of your studies.

00:01:55.159 --> 00:02:01.280
Please do keep engaged with us and provide
feedback so we can continue to improve your

00:02:01.280 --> 00:02:02.600
learning experience.

